article.description: — Gibson Jimerson had 21 points as Saint Louis romped past Central Arkansas 88-65 on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Jimerson lifts Saint Louis past Central Arkansas 88-65
article.linkText: Jimerson lifts Saint Louis past Central Arkansas 88-65
article.story: ST. LOUIS -- — Gibson Jimerson had 21 points as Saint Louis romped past Central Arkansas 88-65 on Tuesday night. Jordan Goodwin had 15 points, 11 rebounds and six steals for Saint Louis (4-0). Yuri Collins added 12 points and nine assists, and Javonte Perkins had 10 points. Rylan Bergersen had 16 points for the Bears (0-3). Jared Chatham added 13 points and DeAndre Jones had 10 points and eight assists. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
